title: Week 1 Studs & Duds + Panic Players, Monday Punday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/12
description:
Fantasy football managers are panicking! On today’s fantasy football podcast, reactions to the Week 1 NFL action! Which surprising studs could do it again, and which dud performances are the most concerning? Plus, big injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 12th, 2022
